# ğŸ“ Exam / Viva Points (Just say this)

âœ” Scaling = increasing/decreasing pod replicas
âœ” `kubectl scale deployment <name> --replicas=n`
âœ” For databases â†’ use StatefulSet in real-world
âœ” For lab demonstration â†’ Deployment scaling is acceptable

